SIMPLE: windage
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Windage
<hw>Wind"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Wind</er>
air in motion.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Gun.)</fld> <def>The difference between the
diameter of the bore of a gun and that of the shot fired from
it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The sudden compression of the air caused by a
projectile in passing close to another body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Windas</ent>⟦br⟧
